I am playing @myth.element Jacksonville. Saturday June 17th 2023. Along with Valdi - Colton Snowden - Mark Lowry b2b Shades

Doors at 9pm.

Hey everyone I am playing tomorrow at @properorl from 9PM - 12AM. Join us as I take you to a journey of my Vinyl collection of deep house, house, progressive house, tribal house, breaks and trance. 
Since my dj career started early 2000 at a place was called Alpha Bar, own by our friend Roger, My love for records began from then on. This is a great opportunity for me to take it back to my roots. 😎
Introducing: A Proper Sunday Experience “Good Spirits”. @djcarlosmendoza is LIVE tonight, selections by Juanderful @e.rave.n @gracesmileyface

Join us this Saturday at @properorl 😎
I have been waiting to do a Special b2b Vinyl Set with my boy @clifftangredi 
If you remember we was the residents djs of Zinc Bar for many years and now we have the privilege to take you back when everything started. 
Don’t call it a reunion, call it a celebration of life.

I am playing this Saturday in Jacksonville Florida, @myth.element Grab your tickets today @eventbrite

Hello everyone! @shade_techno and friends are in the process of organizing an exciting new weekly event at @henaocenter in Orlando. Our aim is to establish a vibrant hub and gathering spot for enthusiasts of techno music, dancers, lovers of the electronic music scene, and DJs alike. Commencing this upcoming Friday, August 18, 2023, the doors will swing open at 10pm, marking the start of this thrilling venture.

Secure your tickets for the upcoming shows!
